{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "They tested the pipeline on two under-resourced agglutinating languages such as Bantu language ISI and the Dravidian language Malayalam Zulu using training data from Google Knowledge Graph and Wikipedia.",
    "The authors also achieved with an average value of F1 score is 78% for Malayalam and an average value of F1 score is 87% for isiZulu.",
    "Liu et al. [105] demonstrated a mixed deep learning strategy to increase the accuracy of NER's identification in biomedical.",
    "They used the Bidirectional Encoder representations from Transformers (BERT) [71] model to identify the text's fundamental attributes, finds out a representation of the text's context using BiLSTM, as well as the multi-head attention (MHATT) mechanism to extract chapter-level features.",
    "An experimental review using a publicly accessible dataset shows that the suggested hybrid technique performs much better at detecting abbreviations, polysemes, and low-frequency entities when compared to state-of-theart approaches."
  ],
